{
  "stanzas": [
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "number": 1,
          "text": "Long upon the mountains weary,"
        },
        {
          "number": 2,
          "text": "Have the scattered flocks been torn;"
        },
        {
          "number": 3,
          "text": "Dark the dessert paths, and dreary;"
        },
        {
          "number": 4,
          "text": "Grievous trials have they borne."
        },
        {
          "number": 5,
          "text": "Now the gathering call is sounding,"
        },
        {
          "number": 6,
          "text": "Solemn in its warning voice;"
        },
        {
          "number": 7,
          "text": "Union, faith, and love, abounding,"
        },
        {
          "number": 8,
          "text": "Bid the little flock rejoice."
        }
      ],
      "number": 1
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "number": 1,
          "text": "Now the light of truth they’re seeking,"
        },
        {
          "number": 2,
          "text": "In its onward track pursue;"
        },
        {
          "number": 3,
          "text": "All the ten commandments keeping,"
        },
        {
          "number": 4,
          "text": "They are holy, just, and true."
        },
        {
          "number": 5,
          "text": "On the words of lire they’re feeding,"
        },
        {
          "number": 6,
          "text": "Precious to their taste so sweet;"
        },
        {
          "number": 7,
          "text": "All their Master’s percepts heeding,"
        },
        {
          "number": 8,
          "text": "Bowing humbly to His feet."
        }
      ],
      "number": 2
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "number": 1,
          "text": "In that light of light and beauty,"
        },
        {
          "number": 2,
          "text": "In that golden city fair,"
        },
        {
          "number": 3,
          "text": "Soon its pearly gates they’ll enter,"
        },
        {
          "number": 4,
          "text": "And of all its glories share."
        },
        {
          "number": 5,
          "text": "There, divine the soul’s expansions;"
        },
        {
          "number": 6,
          "text": "Free from sin, and death, and pain;"
        },
        {
          "number": 7,
          "text": "Tear will never dim those mansions"
        },
        {
          "number": 8,
          "text": "Where the souls immortal reign."
        }
      ],
      "number": 3
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "number": 1,
          "text": "Soon He comes! With clouds descending;"
        },
        {
          "number": 2,
          "text": "All His saints, entombed arise;"
        },
        {
          "number": 3,
          "text": "The redeemed, in anthems blending,"
        },
        {
          "number": 4,
          "text": "Shout their vict’ry thro’ the skies."
        },
        {
          "number": 5,
          "text": "O, we long for Thine appearing;"
        },
        {
          "number": 6,
          "text": "Come, O Savior, quickly come!"
        },
        {
          "number": 7,
          "text": "Blessed hope! Our spirits cheering,"
        },
        {
          "number": 8,
          "text": "Take thy ransomed children home."
        }
      ],
      "number": 4
    }
  ],
  "title": "Long Upon the Mountains"
}
